description.narrative: By 2021, Country Offices have strengthened technical capacity to respond to violence, sexual abuse and exploitation through strengthened formal and informal child protection systems., which contributes to Access To Justice, Prevention And Response Services For Violence Against Children. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Every Child is protected from Violence, Exploitation and Harmful Practices.
